ygData.messageBody:
hi, this is Beld from Fennin Ro! out of curiosity, has anybody else been
able to complete the SK quest in freeport that involves getting an item off
of Lady Shea? i've been killing her for a week, no item, already posted it
as a broken quest but just want to be sure. by the way, even if you dont do
the quest, she is worth killing as she only affects factions in felwithe
(where you are already KoS) and she carries between 2 and 11 PLAT on her
every time ;) just make sure you are at least lvl 15 and free with harm
touch.. she's mean

catch you around,

Beld
